《辐射》在发售当年即获得媒体和玩家总体非常正面的评价，於1997年獲[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]頒發“年度角色扮演遊戲獎”。<ref name="gspot_rpgyear">{{cite web | title = Fallout 2 Previews | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | url = http://www.gamespot.com/pc/rpg/fallout2/news.html?mode=dprdseviews&tag=tabs%3Bpreviews | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | quote=Greg Kasavin finds out what's in store for the sequel to GameSpot's 1997 RPG of the Year, including story details and tons of screenshots.}}</ref>它亦被提名[[互动艺术与科学学会|互动艺术与科学学会]]互動成就獎的“年度電腦角色扮演遊戲獎”和“聲音和音樂的傑出成就獎”。<ref name="1st_interactive">{{cite web|title=1998 1st Interactive Achievement Awards|url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/1998_1st_awards.asp|publisher=Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences|accessdate=2011-12-29|year=1998|archive-date=2013-03-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6F8z12qEi?url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/1998_1st_awards.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《辐射》常被认为在电脑游戏发展史上占有重要地位。《[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]》分別於2001年、2005年、2007年、2008年和2010年將此遊戲列為「史上最佳電腦遊戲」第4<ref name="pcgamer_award_4">{{Citation | title = 50 Best Games of All Time | journal = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |date=October 2001}}</ref>、第10<ref name="pcgamer_award_3">{{Citation | title = 50 Best Games of All Time | journal = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |date=April 2005}}</ref>、第13<ref name="pcgamer_award_2">{{cite web | title = PC Gamer's Best 100 | publisher = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | date = 2007-08-13 | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=169961&site=pcg | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | archive-date = 2013-03-21 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6FHCRVA7n?url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/169961/features/pc-gamers-best-100-50-01/?site=pcg | dead-url = no }}</ref>、第21<ref name="pcgamer_award_5">{{cite web | title = PC Gamer's Top 100 | publisher = ''[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]'' | date = 2008-08-05 | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=194593 | accessdate = 2010-11-16 | archive-date = 2013-03-21 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6FHCSilxw?url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/194593/features/pc-gamers-top-100-part-4/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>和第7位。<ref name="pcgamer_award_1">{{cite web | title = PC Gamer's top 100 PC Games of all time | publisher = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | date = 2010-02-05 | url = http://www.gamesradar.com/f/pc-gamers-top-100-pc-games-of-all-time/a-2010012911133649022/p-5 | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | archive-date = 2013-03-21 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6FHCUT8pf?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/pc-gamers-top-100-pc-games-of-all-time/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]亦分別於2007年和2009年將此遊戲列為「史上最佳電腦遊戲」第5<ref name="ign_award_1">{{cite web | author=Adams, Dan; Butts, Steve; Onyett, Charles | date=2007-03-16 | title=Top 25 PC Games of All Time | publisher=IGN | url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/772/772285p1.html | accessdate=2009-03-20 | archive-date=2013-03-21 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FHCW1Lot?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/03/16/top-25-pc-games-of-all-time | dead-url=no }}</ref>和第19位。<ref name="ign_award_4">{{cite web | author=Ocampo, Jason; Butts, Steve; Haynes, Jeff | date=2009-08-06 | title=Top 25 PC Games of All Time | publisher=IGN | url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/101/1011624p1.html | accessdate=2010-01-03 | archive-date=2012-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622234819/http://pc.ign.com/articles/101/1011624p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[PC_Zone|PC Zone]]則於2007年將此遊戲列為「史上最佳電腦遊戲」第21位。<ref name="pczone_award_1">{{cite web | title = The 101 best PC games ever | publisher = ''[[PC_Zone|PC Zone]]'' | date = 2007-05-20 | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=d164289&site=pcz | accessdate = 2010-11-15}}</ref>IGN亦於2005年和2007年將此遊戲列為「史上最佳遊戲」第55。<ref name="ign_award_2">{{Cite web |url=http://top100.ign.com/2005/index.html |title=IGN's Top 100 Games<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227082124/http://top100.ign.com/2005/index.html |archive-date=2009-02-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和第33位。<ref name="ign_award_3">[http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_3dd3.html IGN Top 100 Games 2007 |33 Fallout<!-- Bot genderated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130127020732/http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_3dd3.html |date=2013-01-27 }}</ref>随着这部作品的成功，《辐射》至今（2016年）已推出3部续集，成为业界最重要的角色扮演游戏品牌之一。

《辐射》已經入選多個遊戲相關組織的“光榮榜”，其中包括《[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]》<ref name="cgw_hof">{{cite web | title = CGW's Hall of Fame | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | url = http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offsewt=3&cId=3139081#23 | accessdate = 2010-11-17 | archive-date = 2013-03-27 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6FQya8PNd?url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offsewt=3#23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、GameSpot<ref name="gspot_award">{{cite web | title=The Greatest Games of all Time | url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgdames/ | accessdate=2010-11-17 }}</ref>、[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]<ref name="gspy_hof">{{cite web | last = Buecheler | first = Christopher | title = The GameSpy Hall of Fame: Fallout | publisher = [[GameSpy|GameSpy]] | date = 2000-12-30 | url = http://www.gamespy.com/contact-us.html | accessdate = 2010-11-17 | archive-date = 2010-11-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101115175639/http://www.gamespy.com/contact-us.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>和IGN。<ref name="ign_hof">{{cite web | title = IGN Videogame Hall Of Fame: Fallout | publisher = IGN | year = 2008 | url = http://games.ign.com/halloffame/fallout.html | accessdate = 2010-11-20 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6FQybcCTU?url=http://games.ign.com/halloffame/fallout.html | archive-date = 2013-03-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>另外，此遊戲的結局和世界亦於2000年被GameSpot列為十大最佳遊戲結局<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_bestending/page2.html |title=Internet Archive Wayback Machine |publisher=Web.archive.org |date=2000-03-02 |accessdate=2012-08-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000302020853/http://www.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_bestending/page2.html |archivedate=2000-03-02 }}</ref>和十大最佳遊戲世界<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_worlds/world3.html |title=Internet Archive Wayback Machine |publisher=Web.archive.org |date=2004-10-26 |accessdate=2012-08-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041026150630/http://www.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_worlds/world3.html |archivedate=2004-10-26 }}</ref>，而開端則於2008年獲《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》列為十大最佳遊戲開端的第六位。<ref name="ginfo_award">"The Top Ten Video Game Openings," ''Game Informer'' 187 (November 2008): 38.</ref>

游戏中出场的队友一条叫“{{le|狗肉 (辐射)|Dogmeat|狗肉}}”的狗，原本只是作为配角出场且按照游戏设计几乎必死无疑（狗肉会无条件跟随玩家且不能命令其离队，“标准死法”是因盲目跟随而被军事基地的力场烤熟，狗肉的牺牲甚至被载入辐射2手册序章，即辐射1的[[官方结局|官方结局]]），然而这个狗角色却出乎开发者意料的受到玩家极大欢迎，有玩家想出创意十足的方法保证狗肉活到游戏通关并公布到黑岛BBS上，这个细节在辐射2做为花絮被披露。结果是，“狗肉”成了辐射系列游戏的第二吉祥物（仅次于避难所小子），以不同面貌出现在以后各代辐射游戏里（包括Bethesda接手后的作品）。“狗肉”甚至上榜Gamespot评选的“历史十大游戏名狗”<ref>{{cite web
